de.oaam.model.oaam.anatomy

Interface Location

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, ModeDependentElementA, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, ResourceProviderInstanceA, VariantDependentElementA
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocationImpl

    public interface Location
extends ResourceProviderInstanceA, ElementA, VariantDependentElementA, ModeDependentElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Location'. A location is a place to install devices or cables.

    The following features are supported:

    • Type
    • Position
    • Duct Openings
    See Also:
    AnatomyPackage.getLocation()
